text: Sony Entertainment Television India is an Indian Hindi-language general entertainment television channel. It broadcast shows like, Aadalat, C.I.D, Bhoot Aaya, Maharana Pratap, Kya Hua Tera Vaada, Behyad, The Kapil Sharma Show, Hasil and Prithvi Vallabh. The channel was launched on 8 November 1995, the Indian television channel is owned by Sony Pictures Networks. ==References== Category:Television channels in India Category:1995 establishments in Asia
title: Sony Entertainment Television
